<br>
Here's some examples:<br>
<br>
Lvl 50 druid I shit you not in prekunark times didn't know where the king room was in Sol B.<br>
<br>
Was in a group camping the ghoul supplier and assassin.  Had weird agro through the floor and we get a train from the savant's room and every frog between there up at our camp.  Everybody is dyiing, we're going down.  People shout EVAC EVAC!!!  Druid self gates out.  When asked why he didn't evac, druid asks whats evac?<br>
<br>
In a group and we get a big pull.  Cleric heals dyiing puller and gets mass agro and needs a heal bad.  Cleric tries to back up and root back up and root, tanks are taunting trying to get the mobs off him.  Cleric being interrupted can't heal himself, hes going down and we can't save him.  Then I think WTF is the druid doing, why isn't he healing the cleric??  I look and the druid is kiting one of the damn frogloks around and attracts MORE mobs.  <br>
<br>
If there's one thing I can't stand its incompetence.  It drives me batty when I'm surrounded by stupid people.  Not making this a slam to all druid players out there at all.   <p>----------------------- <BR>
Zartuul the Tactician <BR>
